Package it.polimi.ingsw.ps19.message.replies

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompleteMarketReply
    Gives the player the market with all orders available
    ConnectionReply
    Reply to a request of connection from a new client
    DrawBusinessCardReply
    Reply to a draw business card action
    ElectCouncillorReply
    Response to a elect councillor action Gives the player updated information
    EndGameReply
    Notifies the player that the game has ended
    EndTurnReply
    Message to notify that a player has ended his turn
    GameStartedMessage
    Message to notify the player that their game has started
    GetBusinessCardOrCityBonusReply
    Message to have the player execute the get business or city bonus
    GetBusinessToDrawReply
    Message to let the player execute the get Business bonus
    PlayerDisconnectedReply
    Notifies all the other players that a player has disconnected
    Reply
    OVERVIEW: The Class Reply is the first child of Message class.
    SendFullGameReply
    Sends the full game info to the player
    SendFullPlayerReply
    OVERVIEW: The Class SendFullPlayerReply is the most used Reply that add an update version of a list of players.
    StringMessage
    The Class StringMessage is used to send only a string message.
    TimeToMarketReply
    Tells the player it is time to make an order
    WaitingPlayerForMarketReply
    Message to wait for the other players to finish their orders
